Step 24: Create CloudStack Source List

24: sudo nano /etc/apt/sources.list.d/cloudstack.list

24.1: Visit CloudStack official guide.

24.2: Paste:  deb https://download.cloudstack.org/ubuntu focal 4.18
24.3: Save and exit.
Step 25: Add CloudStack Public Key
wget -O - https://download.cloudstack.org/release.asc | sudo tee /etc/apt/trusted.gpg.d/cloudstack.asc
Step 26-27: Update Repos
sudo apt update
sudo apt-get update
Step 28: Install CloudStack Management
sudo apt install cloudstack-management
